Final Solution
{{finalsolutions}}
Sometimes you have just gone too far. You can't take back the dramabomb you unleashed on [[customers_suck]], you can't [[ohbutyouwillpet|unfuck a six-month-old]], and you can't turn back time until before you [[User:Jacknstock|blocked someone]] [[User:Crayolacrime|with root access]]. In these unfortunate events you must turn to a '''final solution''' ([[Nazi|German]]:  ''Die Endl√∂sung der Judenfrage''). Not to be confused with a [[last measure]] or [[Catnarok|final destiny]].

In other words, the Final Solution means once and for all eliminating the Jewish problem. Or, if you are a Jew, the Palestinian problem.

==Before using a final solution==

* If your problem is small enough, making your journal [[friends only]] might calm things down.
* Large amounts of [[alcohol]] may solve your problem.
* Consider [[Buy a Dog|buying a dog]].
* [[Jesus]] may be the answer, but most likely [[raptor jesus|isn't]].
* LSD can help you return into a nearly-dreamed state of happiness. Just don't forget [[Fucked up|you may end up a little dizzy]].
* Try doing a [[Barrel Roll|barrel roll]].
* Try cooking a couple of eggs. Well, it gets [[Moot]] excited.

